# Hello Notion Supabase

- Use Supabase MCP for migrations (`apply_migration`), schema inspection (`list_tables`), and project URL/keys.
- Migration names: snake_case (e.g. `add_widgets_table`).
- Auth: anon key for FE with RLS; service role or JWT for BE only; never expose service role to client.
- BE (Kotlin): connect via PostgREST (HTTP) or JDBC (server-only); keep connection details in env.
